# portfolio

## description

A portfolio that is the main hub for showcasing my skills and corresponding projects that apply those skills. This portfolio will also be housed on a live server that will allow people to access, interact, and view from their own computer or device. As I complete more projects or gain new skills the site will be updated as well.

## built with

-   HTML
-   CSS

## contributing 

Please feel free to clone the git repo and create your own feature branchs off the main branch to apply your own improvements or recommendations to the website.
